# Code
```
class Solution {

    public boolean digitCount(String num) {
        Map<Integer, Integer> occurrence = new HashMap<>(num.length());
        for (int i = 0; i < num.length(); i++) {
            int currentDigit = num.charAt(i) - '0';
            occurrence.put(currentDigit, occurrence.getOrDefault(currentDigit, 0) + 1);
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < num.length(); i++) {
            int currentDigit = num.charAt(i) - '0';
            int count = 0;
            if (occurrence.containsKey(i)) {
                count = occurrence.get(i);
            }
            if (count != currentDigit) {
                return false;
            }
        }

        return true;
    }
}
```

