# Approach
- Sort the portions array in ascending order.
- Iterate over the spells array and for each spells[i], find the minimum required potion for it. 
- Check for the index of potion in potions array using binary search to find the number of potions greter than required.
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(nlogn)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: O(n)
